profile: Established in 2007, Canadian Appliance Source, also known as CAS, quickly became the largest independent appliance retailer in Ontario.When looking to purchase home and kitchen appliances for your new house, remodeled kitchen or a rental property, CAS has it is all.With hundreds of appliances shipped daily, fully-stocked showrooms, and three distribution centers nationwide Canadian Appliance Source is the leading dealer of consumer appliances in Canada.Our success has been built on a simple principle: take care of every customer as if they are a member of our own family.In addition to having 15+ showrooms, we are one of the few independent appliance e-commerce dealers in Canada fully authorized to sell household appliances online. This allows you to shop from the comfort of your home while benefiting from cost-saving rebates that our competitors can't offer.All our products come with a minimum of one-year manufacturer’s warranty (some exceptions apply). This provides peace of mind knowing that our products are fully backed with the support of the manufacturer.How can we can afford to offer such low pricing? Because of the sheer volume of our sales, we can negotiate rock-bottom pricing with our distributors. We then pass these savings on to you through our low prices.

profile: Deco Solutions specializes in the installation of kitchen cabinet doors and refinishing (refacing) the outside of existing cabinets. Visit our website at http//decosolutions.ca. We can also add new drawers, moldings and more. All this is done within 2-3 days and at a cost of 40% less of a new kitchen. We can add brand new cabinet doors, drawer fronts and countertops and finalize the restoration by also adding decorative elements such as moldings, light valances, handles and much more. The look of your kitchen is rapidly improved in a fraction of the time!
